en_838594_0	Reconstruction of Meda Oyamaduwa tank in Mahavilalchchiya is slated to commence tomorrow under the patronage of Prime Minister Ranil ckremasinghe.
en_838594_1	The reconstruction will be undertaken under the Climate friendly Irrigation Project mooted by the Ministry of Irrigation and Agriculture.
en_838594_2	The estimated expenditure on the project is five million rupees.
en_838594_3	It is planned to reconstruct the Meda Oyamaduwa tank bund, preparation of the bunds and the removal of silt.
en_838594_4	A large number of farmer families in the area will benefit.
